<p>将字符串数组中的<code v-pre>字母异位词</code>组合在一起，如：</p>
<p>input: <code v-pre>strs = [&quot;eat&quot;, &quot;tea&quot;, &quot;tan&quot;, &quot;ate&quot;, &quot;nat&quot;, &quot;bat&quot;]</code></p>
